@Descr
There are (better) algorithms for

<UL>
<LI>
Gcd over algebraic extensions of Q (Encarnacion)
<LI>
Factorization of polynomials over Q (van Hoeij)
<LI>
Factorization of polynomials over local fields
</UL>

It would be useful to have these available.

@Ref
<UL>
<LI>
M. J. Encarnaci\'on, J. Symbolic Comput. {\bf 20} (1995), no.~3, 299--313;
MR 97c:11117
<LI>
H. Cohen, {\it A course in computational algebraic number theory},
Springer, Berlin, 1993; MR 94i:11105
<LI>
M. v.Hoeij, {\it Factoring Polynomials and the knapsack problem},
<A HREF="http://www.math.fsu.edu/~hoeij/papers.html">see here</A>.
<LI>
S. Pauli, Factoring Polynomials over local fields, J.Symb.Comp. 32 (2001),
533-547
</UL>
@Rem
Rudimentary multivariate factorization will be available in 4.5.
